snippet.title: BAYC’s Next Chapter - What You Need to Know About Sewer Passes, the Skilled-Based Mint, and More.
snippet.description:
Here is your video explainer covering the key information for the next activations of the Jimmy The Monkey rollout, including details on Sewer Pass claim, Dookey Dash, and more to prepare you for the skill-based mint that will be live from Jan. 18th until Feb. 8th on https://mdvmm.xyz. 

Explore The Swamp Below:

BAYC Website: https://www.boredapeyachtclub.com 

MDvMM site: https://mdvmm.xyz

BAYC Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/@boredapeyc
